  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/8a6eb896fb049eb16a24a02f173c383f.avif?t=1720751095\" width=706 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >产品介绍</h2>《相亲攻略：宝贝别再选了我》是一款恋爱模拟的真人互动剧，讲述关于“你”的相亲故事。<br>从接到母亲电话开始，你踏上相亲之旅，和你预想的不一样，苦恼的事情并不是如何找到一个对象，而是……这么多对象该带哪一个回家。<br><br>①号女嘉宾：冷面女总裁 陈映<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/41e06479bd68460278897e4a94fcdc24.poster.avif?t=1720751095\" width=620 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/41e06479bd68460278897e4a94fcdc24.webm?t=1720751095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/41e06479bd68460278897e4a94fcdc24.mp4?t=1720751095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“我也就在你面前装装贤良淑德。”<br><br>②号女嘉宾：古灵精少女 江彤彤<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/354e7723a89efde68555a1a1127dfd50.poster.avif?t=1720751095\" width=656 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/354e7723a89efde68555a1a1127dfd50.webm?t=1720751095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/354e7723a89efde68555a1a1127dfd50.mp4?t=1720751095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“你不是癞蛤蟆吃天鹅肉，咱是俩癞蛤蟆抱着互啃。”<br><br>③号女嘉宾：风情美妇 叶小曼<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/5cf64dbd01dde27e8d46a3dc710a1af9.poster.avif?t=1720751095\" width=620 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/5cf64dbd01dde27e8d46a3dc710a1af9.webm?t=1720751095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/5cf64dbd01dde27e8d46a3dc710a1af9.mp4?t=1720751095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“你知道的，我永远都不会拒绝你的。”<br><br>④号女嘉宾：贤良佳人 林静婉<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/d5eb5b224c5d68a783ad27fc87c00958.poster.avif?t=1720751095\" width=620 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/d5eb5b224c5d68a783ad27fc87c00958.webm?t=1720751095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/d5eb5b224c5d68a783ad27fc87c00958.mp4?t=1720751095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“你饿不饿，我做碗面给你吃。”<br><br>⑤号女嘉宾：呆萌女教授 柳舒月<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/55063536df7ed303082efdad6fb0c4d9.poster.avif?t=1720751095\" width=620 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/55063536df7ed303082efdad6fb0c4d9.webm?t=1720751095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/55063536df7ed303082efdad6fb0c4d9.mp4?t=1720751095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“我还有课题没有做，所以请跟我结婚吧。”<br><br>⑥号女嘉宾：病娇小护士 李心怡<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/b34730f413452bf97d9746a1b5550bd8.poster.avif?t=1720751095\" width=620 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/b34730f413452bf97d9746a1b5550bd8.webm?t=1720751095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958700/extras/b34730f413452bf97d9746a1b5550bd8.mp4?t=1720751095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“只要是你的东西，哪怕是你的影子，我都要留住。”<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >相亲相关</h2>相亲是平等的灵魂相互沟通，寻找爱的可能，可由于现实的种种原因，很大程度变成了单方面的筛选。<br>《相亲攻略》希望能让玩家能在其中收获尊重和爱，体验一段美好的相亲之旅。<br><i>今年过年记得带对象回家……如果没有，也要好好的。</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特别说明</h2>没有一场相亲是在准备周全以后开始的，《相亲攻略》同样也是，若有错误或缺漏之处还请包涵，等待后续的修复与版本迭代。",
